 and pure steam generators. It also offers equipment installation, maintenance, upgradation, repair, and troubleshooting services; and preventive maintenance programs and repair services. It serves its products and services to hospitals, other healthcare providers, and pharmaceutical manufacturers. The company was founded in 1985 and is headquartered in Mentor, Ohio.", "fullTimeEmployees": 17787, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Daniel A. Carestio", "age": 51, "title": "President, CEO & Director", "yearBorn": 1973, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 2284218, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 9352543}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Michael J. Tokich", "age": 55, "title": "Senior VP & CFO", "yearBorn": 1969, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 1078165, "exercisedValue": 11214015, "unexercisedValue": 6296034}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. John Adam Zangerle", "age": 57, "title": "Senior VP, General Counsel & Secretary", "yearBorn": 1967, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 943792, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 9452866}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Mary Clare Fraser", "age": 54, "title": "SVP & Chief Human Resources Officer", "yearBorn": 1970, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 725668, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 140335}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Cary L. Majors", "age": 49, "title": "Senior VP & President of Healthcare", "yearBorn": 1975, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 861813, "exercisedValue": 569217, "unexercisedValue": 1810847}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Karen L. Burton", "age": 56, "title": "VP & Chief Accounting Officer", "yearBorn": 1968, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Julie  Winter", "title": "Vice President of Investor Relations & Corporate Communications", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Julia K. Madsen", "age": 59, "title": "Senior VP & GM of Life Sciences", "yearBorn": 1965, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue":